{"'Arrays must have the same length'":"E0","`HTTP ${response.status}`":"E1","'No response body to stream'":"E2","'string notation required for auto precision.'":"E3","INPUT_ERROR":"E4","FINALIZE_ERROR":"E5","'Illegal argument ' + message":"E6","'Invalid data'":"E7","'The amount of data is too big to be stored in a QR Code'":"E8","'\\n' +\n      'The chosen QR Code version cannot contain this amount of data.\\n' +\n      'Minimum version required to store current data is: ' + bestVersion + '.\\n'":"E9","'No input text'":"E10","'Encoder not initialized'":"E11","'\"' + data + '\"' +\n      ' cannot be encoded with mode ' + Mode.toString(mode) +\n      '.\\n Suggested mode is: ' + Mode.toString(bestMode)":"E12","'\"version\" cannot be null or undefined'":"E13","'\"version\" should be in range from 1 to 40'":"E14","'\"toSJISFunc\" is not a valid function.'":"E15","'Invalid QR Code version'":"E16","ed[0]":"E17","msg || ec[ind]":"E18","message.error":"E19","'Invalid JSON response from server'":"E20","'The provider is not valid.'":"E21","'store timed out'":"E22","msg":"E23","\"Cannot find module '\"+o+\"'\"":"E24","'resolver must be a function'":"E25","'Cannot resolve promise with itself'":"E26","'must be an array'":"E27","\"Cannot call a class as a function\"":"E28","'Failed to get type for BinaryArray'":"E29","'Unkown type: ' + type":"E30","\"Can't call config() after localforage \" + 'has been used.'":"E31","'Database version must be a number.'":"E32","'Custom driver not compliant; see ' + 'https://mozilla.github.io/localForage/#definedriver'":"E33","'Method ' + methodName + ' is not implemented by the current driver'":"E34","'Driver not found.'":"E35","'No available storage method found.'":"E36"}